    "attribution": {
        "Notes and update by Lotus06.txt": "NOTE: [Unlock All Special fusion ON] allows you to fuse all special fusion demons without having the required demons to fuse them! So all special fusion demons practically just cost you macca to get them! :D\n\n[All Essences are available during Essence Fusion] unlocks all essences in the game during essence fusion only!",
        "SHIN MEGAMI TENSEI V.txt": "by Hazerou\nBetter use lower Resolution to achieve stable 60 FPS.\n\nIncluded in the text file;\n\n[Upscale Quality] <= NEW!\n[Enable / Disable Dynamic Resolution]\n[RRS]\n[Image Sharpening]\n[Vignette]\n[Outlines]\n[Motion Blur]\n[Film Grain]\n[CHROM AB]\n[Lens Flare]\n[Sky Lighting Quality]\n[Adaptive Exposure]\n[View Distance Scale]\n[DOF]\n[Anisotropic Filtering]\n[MSAA]\n[AA]\n[Shadow]\n[Shadow Distance]\n[SSAO]\n[Bloom]\n[MIN/MAX/Default GFX Quality]\n\nNote;\n\nThe [GFX Quality] Are For;\n\n[Adaptive Exposure]\n[View Distance Scale]\n[DOF]\n[Anisotropic Filtering]\n[MSAA]\n[AA]\n[Shadow]\n[Shadow Distance]\n[SSAO]\n[Bloom]\n\n=====\n\n[Upscale Quality] Is noticeable (more usable) when using lower RRS + AA OFF, AA Very Low or AA Low.\n\nType-0: Nearest filtering\n\nType-1: Simple Bilinear\n\nType-2: Directional blur with unsharp mask upsample.\n\nType-3: 5-tap Catmull-Rom bicubic, approximating Lanczos 2. (default)\n\nType-4: 13-tap Lanczos 3.\n\nType-5: 36-tap Gaussian-filtered unsharp mask (very expensive, but good for extreme upsampling)\n\n\n[RRS] is Render Resolution Scale and it disables Dynamic Resolution Function.\nPlease use;\nHandheld RRS for Handheld Mode.\nDocked RRS for Docked Mode.\nAnd please don't activate both at the same time!\n\nSome GFX Codes has no Function/Effect to the Game. \n"
    },
